            <note>Avraham, Zekharyah and David ben Shelomoh ben David at-Ṭabīʻah, inscribed in the colophon, folio 138v. 
								Lulwah (?) bat Ḥasan at-Ṭabīʻah and Ibrahim ibn Da'ud, inscribed in the contract of sale with a date of 22 Sivan 165 (1654) and the names of three witnesses; in Judeo-Arabic, folio 138v. A list of previous owners' names, undated, folio 1r. </note>
